                    <p class="text-gray-600">Focus on whole foods: vegetables, fruits, lean proteins, and whole grains. Try the "plate method": fill half your plate with non-starchy veggies, a quarter with lean protein, and a quarter with high-fiber carbs. Limit sugary drinks and processed snacks.</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Card 2: Physical Activity -->
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
